        <p>Number of core plasmidome genes (<italic>y</italic> axis) grouped into COG categories (<italic>x</italic> axis) from each plasmidome population (<italic>n</italic> = 9). Download <inline-supplementary-material id="fS6" mimetype="application" mime-subtype="x-eps" xlink:href="mBio.03284-19-sf006.eps" content-type="local-data">FIG S6, EPS file, 0.2 MB</inline-supplementary-material>.</p>
